ement for parallel AI agent workflows\r\n\r\nUsage: \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mwt\u001b[0m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;6m[OPTIONS]\u001b[0m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;6m[COMMAND]\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;2mCommands:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mswitch\u001b[0m  Switch to a worktree; create if needed\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mlist\u001b[0m    List worktrees and their status\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mremove\u001b[0m  Remove worktree; delete branch if merged\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mmerge\u001b[0m   Merge current branch into the target branch\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mstep\u001b[0m    Run individual operations\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mhook\u001b[0m    Run configured hooks\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6mconfig\u001b[0m  Manage user & project configs\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;2mOptions:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m-h\u001b[0m, \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m--help\u001b[0m     Print help (see more with '--help')\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m-V\u001b[0m, \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m--version\u001b[0m  Print version\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;2mGlobal Options:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m-C\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;6m <path>\u001b[0m                Working directory for this command\r\n      \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m--config\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;6m <path>\u001b[0m      User config file path\r\n      \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m--config-set\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;6m <toml>\u001b[0m  Override config with inline TOML, e.g. --config-set list.full=true (repeatable)\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m-v\u001b[0m, \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;6m--verbose\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;6m...\u001b[0m         Verbose output (-v: info logs + hook/alias template variables on stderr; -vv: also debug logs and raw subprocess \r\n    output written to .git/wt/logs/). Set WORKTRUNK_VERBOSE=0|1|2 to apply the same level everywhere — in